### Test 1: Hello endpoint (Public)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/users/hello

### Test 2: Info endpoint (Public)
GET http://localhost:8085/api/auth/info

### Test 3: Register ADMIN (Public)
POST http://localhost:8085/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "email": "admin@wordly.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "ADMIN",
  "nom": "Admin",
  "prenom": "System",
  "telephone": "+216 12345678",
  "poste": "Directeur"
}

